@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Discover Jordan";
}
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<body>
    <header>
        @Html.Partial("_Header")
    </header>
    <style>

        .first img {
            width: auto;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .first h3 {
            font-family: Cursive;
        }


        .row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between; /* Adjust alignment as needed */
            flex-wrap: wrap; /* Allow items to wrap to the next line if the width is not enough */
        }

        .column {
            width: calc(33.33% - 20px); /* Adjust width and margin as needed */
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 10px; /* Added margin between columns */
            margin-bottom: 20px; /* Added margin between rows */
        }

        img {
            border-radius: 8px;
        }



        .button-22:active {
            background-color: #006AE8;
        }

        .button-22:hover {
            background-color: #1C84FF;
        }

        .text12 {
            font-family: cursive;
        }

        .sectext {
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
            text-align: center;
        }


        .scuba-diving-course {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 50px 0;
        }

        .scuba-diving-experience {
            width: 25%;
            margin: 10px;
            text-align: left;
			background: linear-gradient(to right,#e0e0e0 , #fcfcfc );
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

            .scuba-diving-experience img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
            }


            .scuba-diving-experience h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
                margin-top: 10px;
            }

            .scuba-diving-experience p {
                margin-top: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

        .book-now-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .learn-more-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: #000; /* Change text color to black */
            text-decoration: none;
        }

            .learn-more-btn:hover {
                transition: 0.7s;
                background-color: #007bff;
                color: #fff; /* Change text color to white on hover */
            }

        .section-header1 {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .section-header1::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                display: block;
                width: 60px;
                height: 5px;
                bottom: 0;
                left: calc(50% - 25px);
            }

            .section-header1 h2 {
                font-size: 36px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                text-align: center;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: -20px;
            }


        .section-header {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

            .section-header::before {
                content: '';
                position: absolute;
                display: block;
                width: 60px;
                height: 5px;
                background: #f82249;
                bottom: 0;
                left: calc(50% - 25px);
            }

            .section-header h2 {
                font-size: 36px;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                text-align: center;
                font-weight: 700;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }

            .section-header p {
                text-align: center;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
                font-size: 18px;
                font-weight: 500;
                color: #9195a2;
            }

        

    </style>

    <div class="red-box">
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header1">

            <h2>Discover Jordan</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="first">

        <img src="/img/discover.PNG" alt="Discover page" />
    </div>
    <br />
    <br />
    


  


    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Trips</h2>
            <p>Choose your trip</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <section class="scuba-diving-course">
        <div class="scuba-diving-experience">
            <img src="~/img/aqaba.jpg" alt="Aqaba">
            <h2>Trips in Aqaba</h2>
            <p>Start From</p>
            <p>65 JD</p>
            <a href="/Home/Aqaba" class="book-now-btn">Book Now</a>
        </div>


        <div class="scuba-diving-experience">
            <img src="/img/ajloin.jpg" alt="Scuba Diving Experience">
            <h2>Trips in Ajloin</h2>
            <p>Start From</p>
            <p>35 JD</p>
            <a href="#" class="book-now-btn">Book Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="scuba-diving-experience">
            <img src="/img/maein.jpg" alt="Al Haddad Scuba Program">
            <h2>Trips in Ma'in Hot Springs</h2>
            <p>Start From</p>
            <p>15 JD</p>
            <a href="#" class="book-now-btn">Book Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="scuba-diving-experience">
            <img src="/img/rum.jpg" alt="Al Haddad Scuba Program">
            <h2>Trips in Wadi Rum</h2>
            <p>Start From</p>
            <p>29 JD</p>
            <a href="#" class="book-now-btn">Book Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="scuba-diving-experience">
            <img src="/img/JERASH.jpg" alt="Al Haddad Scuba Program">
            <h2>Trips in Jerash</h2>
            <p>Start From</p>
            <p>9 JD</p>
            <a href="#" class="book-now-btn">Book Now</a>
        </div>
        <div class="scuba-diving-experience">
            <img src="/img/deadsea.jpg" alt="Boat & Diving Trip, Jeddah to Bayada Islands">
            <h2>Trips in DeadSea</h2>
            <p>Start From</p>
            <p>69 JD</p>
            <a href="#" class="book-now-btn">Book Now</a>
        </div>


    </section>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2>Explore Jordan</h2>
            <p>Check out best thing to do in jordan</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="column">
            <img src="/img/img1.jpg" alt="Snow" style="width:100%">
            <br />
            <br />
            <figcaption class="text12">Petra is half-built, half-carved into the rock, and is surrounded by mountains riddled with passages and gorges. An ingenious water management system allowed extensive settlement of an essentially arid area during the Nabataean, Roman and Byzantine periods.</figcaption>
            <br />



            <a href="https://www.visitpetra.jo/" target="perta" class="learn-more-btn">Learn More</a>
        </div>


        <div class="column">
            <img src="/img/img2.jpg" alt="Forest" style="width:100%">
            <br />
            <br />
            <figcaption class="text12">Jerash is considered one of the largest and most well-preserved sites of Greek and Roman architecture in the world outside Italy. And is sometimes misleadingly referred to as the "Pompeii of the Middle East" or of Asia, referring to its size, extent of excavation and level of preservation.</figcaption>
            <br />


            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerash" target="jarash" class="learn-more-btn">Learn More</a>
        </div>


        <div class="column">
            <img src="/img/img3.jpg" alt="Mountains" style="width:100%">
            <br />
            <br />
            <figcaption class="text12">The 74,000-hectare property, inscribed as a mixed natural and cultural site, is situated in southern Jordan, near the border with Saudi Arabia. It features a varied desert landscape consisting of a range of narrow gorges, natural arches, towering cliffs, ramps, massive landslides and caverns.</figcaption>
            <br />


            <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wadi_Rum" target="wadirum" class="learn-more-btn">Learn More</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br />
    <br />
    <br />


</body>
</html>
